      <title>Chairperson - OWASP Global Board of Directors</title>
      <link>http://localhost:4322/advisoryboard/owasp/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:4322/advisoryboard/owasp/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Serving on the OWASP Global Board of Directors, including time as Chair of the board - the first female Chair in OWASP&amp;rsquo;s history. Appointed as a Compliance Officer of the OWASP Foundation effective January 1, 2025, continuing to drive governance, global strategy, and community initiatives across the foundation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://owasp.org/corporate/&#34;&gt;https://owasp.org/corporate/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://owasp.org/www-board/&#34;&gt;https://owasp.org/www-board/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
